{"tid":2470532,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[求救]細妹俾人搞大左個肚","createTime":"2021-04-01T03:19:54.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-30T14:37:36.000Z","uid":374134,"like":45,"dislike":847,"uniUserReply":52,"replies":[{"pid":"a0204b4200250448297dd96a22200ebc528e5d22","tid":2470532,"uid":374134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-01T03:19:54.000Z","msg":"我細妹中三 就俾人搞大咗個肚... <br />\n<br />\n因為我細妹本身好MK 我又要番學 根本冇時間管佢既生活 <br />\n<br />\n其實我地屋企從細到大都係咁 <br />\n<br />\n阿爸阿媽番工 放假就係屋企休息 基本上我地兩兄妹只要唔變壞就唔會去管我地 <br />\n<br />\n但係我細妹呢件事太大獲 阿媽激到想辭職留係屋企 管我細妹 <br />\n<br />\n大概係3~4個月前 我細妹佢玩game識到一個男人 <br />\n<br />\n然後果個男人咁岩又住係我地附近 <br />\n<br />\n年紀應該有3X歲 而且離過婚 聽講離婚係因為經常飲醉酒發酒癲 <br />\n<br />\n佢地好似係網上傾咗2~3個禮拜就見面了 <br />\n<br />\n而且第一日見面就上佢屋企啪啪啪了 <br />\n<br />\n之後每個假日 佢地都會見面上佢度啪啪啪 <br />\n<br />\n就係咁一直持續了3個月左右 <br />\n<br />\n我細妹就同果個男人說講 她已經3個月冇黎m <br />\n<br />\n果個男人一開始話佢會負責 會黎我地屋企提親 <br />\n<br />\n估唔到講完呢句話 第二天就人間蒸發 手機都打不通 一直熄機 <br />\n<br />\n直到我細妹前日同我阿爸阿媽講呢件事 <br />\n<br />\n我爸媽前日夜晚12點 就衝去果個男人屋企撞門 <br />\n<br />\n要果個男人講清楚 而且準備告佢 果個男人話佢消失果兩個禮拜 係同朋友出國玩 <br />\n<br />\n咁岩今日番黎 準備要打俾我細妹 我地就衝咗過黎 <br />\n<br />\n我爸媽根本唔信 而且果個男人睇落窮酸樣 又住公屋 邊有錢出國玩 <br />\n<br />\n我細妹就一直喊一直喊 <br />\n<br />\n果晚我阿媽俾咗枝驗孕棒俾我細妹用 真係大咗肚 <br />\n<br />\n琴晚我知道咗件事之後 請咗一日假 同我細妹傾下 <br />\n<br />\n我細妹就話果個男人對佢好好 點點點咁 <br />\n<br />\n我根本就聽唔入耳 我就話 對你好 只不過係想呃你隻豬 <br />\n<br />\n一講完呢句 我細妹就喊 然後將枱面部iPhone掟落地 成個moon爆咗 <br />\n<br />\n所以我想下各位巴打 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n知唔知邊度整番個moon好 <br />\n<br />\nTHX<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"large\"><span class=\"gold\"><strong>Btw.愚人節快樂</strong></span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7dcea1b9a9838ba92f0026730f56d60162704ed7","tid":2470532,"uid":374134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-01T03:21:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/power.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/power.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3d1683514debea3c3d92691c57f70194d845a45","tid":2470532,"uid":155715,"like":17,"dislike":222,"score":-205,"citedBy":7,"replyTime":"2021-04-01T03:22:12.000Z","msg":"部iphone 係無辜架<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2b0491afe799aea8ea923d223855cfa714ed798","tid":2470532,"uid":38298,"like":33,"dislike":0,"score":33,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-01T03:23:07.000Z","msg":"無是咁的零分"},{"pid":"e26274e81d04a87c3eec28c0ba9c30d0cdda31b4","tid":2470532,"uid":110099,"like":142,"dislike":1,"score":141,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-01T03:23:30.000Z","msg":"又翻炒 悶唔悶<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4695a0d3432c78c0cfca3e071d5fa0ec806b48b","tid":2470532,"uid":344567,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"c3d1683514debea3c3d92691c57f70194d845a45","tid":2470532,"uid":155715,"like":17,"dislike":222,"score":-205,"citedBy":7,"replyTime":"2021-04-01T03:22:12.000Z","msg":"部iphone 係無辜架<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-01T03:23:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4303152d37fd51272c4aed836ce82eb4882053e","tid":2470532,"uid":89931,"like":83,"dislike":0,"score":83,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-01T03:23:47.000Z","msg":"回帶得太密 拉"},{"pid":"e8e512968ff1ce7262d44e5efe0baecb1c4ea85e","tid":2470532,"uid":374134,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-01T03:23:56.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"large\"><strong>是咁的</strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/miracle.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/miracle.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/miracle.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb43e942c883260ee7023f50b9016452fdf20c66","tid":2470532,"uid":347528,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-01T03:23:58.000Z","msg":"屌你老母咩<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br